  <prompt>
    **Re-scoped 2026-06-02 per decision record D-01 + owner direction** (which adopted path-b and added the binding constraint that JPS authoring follow `/jps-action-create` + `/jps-playbook-design` skill conventions). The empirical investigation during the previous task-execute attempt surfaced 3 open questions; this task resolves them by reading the authoritative documents that those skills load — `docs/architecture/playbook-architecture.md` + `.claude/catalogs/scope-model-index.json`. These should answer Q1 (sprk_actiontype field shape), Q2 (sprk_actiontypeid lookup target), and Q3 (canvas Designer clobber prevention) without further empirical investigation.
  </prompt>

  <role>Architectural-doc investigator + JPS conventions specialist.</role>

  <goal>
    Three open questions from D-01 §3 resolved with citations to the authoritative docs. Findings recorded in D-01 §3 ("Resolved per playbook-architecture.md") or in a follow-up D-01 update. With Q1+Q2+Q3 answered, downstream tasks 002–008 can proceed cleanly without further architectural ambiguity.
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="decision-record">projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r2/decisions/D-01-wave-b-root-cause-corrected.md (the questions to resolve)</file>
    <file purpose="authoritative-arch">docs/architecture/playbook-architecture.md (loaded by jps-playbook-design Step 2)</file>
    <file purpose="catalog">.claude/catalogs/scope-model-index.json (loaded by jps-playbook-design Step 2)</file>
